    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment accepted despite single factor (Test conditions) falling below required level. The literature-review-based benchmarking of model outputs against published pedicle screw compression-bending data from seventeen peer-reviewed sources provides sufficient supporting evidence. The test conditions gap is acknowledged and risk-accepted given the strong agreement between FEA predictions and the surveyed literature corpus across all three QoIs. Model risk level 3 with medium assurance level is consistent with Class II device decision consequence.",
